rComments: Very disappointed in this class and the professor. There is little to no structure to the class and she fails to give handout and assignment sheets leaving the students confused about what criteria they need to meet for handing in projects. I would not recommend this professor as she is disorganized and confused most of the time.

She is a nice and caring lady. She does try, but it doesn't always work. She gets the TA to do all the teaching and the photo-media tech to assist her with some things. She'll expect students to do presentations about things that she should teach that are not worth anything. The course time isn't managed well. However, her feedback is good.
Smart, but a good prof. It's pretty clear she does not care about teaching. She spends a lot of time getting other people to teach the class (TA's & outside people).

Had her in first year Image in Motion and she was BORING. EVEN MORE boring 4 years later. She assigns artist statements after the crit is done and the TA does all the teaching. (He is a really good TA though.)
